{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"OTPCredential","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OTPCredential","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","browserCompat":["api.OTPCredential"],"baseline":{"baseline":false,"support":{"chrome":"93","chrome_android":"84","edge":"93"}},"sidebarHTML":"<ol><li class=\"section\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebOTP_API\">WebOTP API</a></li><li class=\"section\"><em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OTPCredential\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>OTPCredential</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></em></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Instance properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OTPCredential/code\"><code>code</code></a><abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Credential\"><code>Credential</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for WebOTP API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CredentialsContainer/get\"><code>CredentialsContainer.get()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","sidebarMacro":"APIRef","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard secure\"><p><strong>Secure context:</strong> This feature is available only in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">secure contexts</a> (HTTPS), in some or all <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">supporting browsers</a>.</p></div><div class=\"notecard experimental\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>OTPCredential</code></strong> interface of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebOTP_API\">WebOTP API</a> is returned when a WebOTP <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CredentialsContainer/get\" title=\"navigator.credentials.get()\"><code>navigator.credentials.get()</code></a> call (i.e. invoked with an <code>otp</code> option) fulfills. It includes a <code>code</code> property that contains the retrieved one-time password (OTP).</p><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Credential\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"80\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"40\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      Credential\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"80\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"80,14 90,9 90,19 80,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OTPCredential\" aria-current=\"page\">\n    <rect x=\"110\" y=\"0\" width=\"104\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"162\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      OTPCredential\n    </text>\n  </a></svg>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instance_properties","title":"Instance properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>This interface also inherits properties from <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Credential\"><code>Credential</code></a>.</em></p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"otpcredential.code\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OTPCredential/code\"><code>OTPCredential.code</code></a> <span class=\"badge inline readonly\" title=\"This value may not be changed.\">Read only </span> <abbr class=\"icon icon-experimental\" title=\"Experimental. Expect behavior to change in the future.\">\n    <span class=\"visually-hidden\">Experimental</span>\n</abbr></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The one-time password (OTP).</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"instance_methods","title":"Instance methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The below code triggers the browser's permission flow when an SMS message arrives. If permission is granted, then the promise resolves with an <code>OTPCredential</code> object. The contained <code>code</code> value is then set as the value of an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> form element, which is then submitted.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><div class=\"example-header\"><span class=\"language-name\">js</span></div><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>navigator.credentials\n  .get({\n    otp: { transport: [\"sms\"] },\n    signal: ac.signal,\n  })\n  .then((otp) =&gt; {\n    input.value = otp.code;\n    if (form) form.submit();\n  })\n  .catch((err) =&gt; {\n    console.error(err);\n  });\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"notecard note\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> For a full explanation of the code, see the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebOTP_API\">WebOTP API</a> landing page. You can also <a href=\"https://web-otp.glitch.me/\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">see this code as part of a full working demo</a>.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://wicg.github.io/web-otp/#OTPCredential","title":"WebOTP API"}],"query":"api.OTPCredential"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.OTPCredential"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Instance properties","id":"instance_properties"},{"text":"Instance methods","id":"instance_methods"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The OTPCredential interface of the WebOTP API is returned when a WebOTP navigator.credentials.get() call (i.e. invoked with an otp option) fulfills. It includes a code property that contains the retrieved one-time password (OTP).","popularity":0.0026,"modified":null,"other_translations":[],"pageType":"web-api-interface","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/otpcredential","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/en-us/web/api/otpcredential/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/null","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"OTPCredential","parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"References"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OTPCredential","title":"OTPCredential"}],"pageTitle":"OTPCredential - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false},"url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OTPCredential"}